summary: TL* THE CONTACT OWNS A 2005 JAGUAR S-TYPE. WHILE DRIVING 30 MPH, THE DRIVER SIDE AIR BAG DEPLOYED. TWO MINUTES LATER, THE PASSENGER SIDE AIR BAG DEPLOYED. THE VEHICLE WAS TAKEN TO A DEALER, BUT WAS NOT DIAGNOSED OR REPAIRED. THE VEHICLE WAS NOT REPAIRED. THE MANUFACTURER WAS MADE AWARE OF THE FAILURES. THE APPROXIMATE FAILURE MILEAGE WAS 60,000.
